While stopping container it will send SIGTERM signal to stop running process inside it. After default 10sec grace, send SIGKILL.
Docker-compose can use json also.
docker-compose up to -> start or restart services.
docker-compose run -> to run admin tasks on containers 
docker-compose start -> restarts all services.

Docker build context makes small image if there's no data on current dir. Unless image size wiil be more. 

REXRAY volume plugin for docker. 
